Name: SUR5
About the game: Innovative Gameplay SUR5 brings a brand new, fun experience that is easy to understand, but has surprising depth with many nuances to discover. Free to Play This game DOES NOT have packs that contain random playable cards. All players have an equal chance to have a good time. Freedom of Choice Explore thousands of combinations using 16 unique heroes. Many more are going to be released on a regular schedule. Satisfying Competition SUR5 respects fair gameplay that doesn't rely on crazy turnarounds to be exciting. Mechanics promote knowledge about the game features and taking calculated risks. Underdog Company This project is developed by a small, hard working team with big ambitions. Received support will be used for further game improvements. Survive the apocalypse and become a part of the Rebellion!
